    new "在塔米深夜来到你卧室的那一幕发生几天后，"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:3
    old "Suzy will call you for help in the evening."
    new "苏茜会在傍晚打电话向你求助。"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:47
    old "Don't worry, it'll be fine"
    new "别担心，没事的"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:51
    old "Let me take a look at it"
    new "让我看看"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:54
    old "Maybe don't drive like a crazy person?"
    new "也许别像疯子一样开车？"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:94
    old "I didn't mind"
    new "我不在意"

    # game/Scenes/Suzy/suzy5.rpy:105
    old "No, probably not"
    new "不，大概不会"

